snippet.textDisplay: This narration talks about social distancing as if it was really that easy. Even with the pandemic on-going, life also goes on. And that means that for majority of us who can’t afford the ‘luxury’ of driving a car HAVE TO take the subway to go to work. Not all industries can also afford the luxury of putting most or all of their employees to work from home. So it is somewhat inevitable but what this article could have improved on is to also highlight other aspects that come into context when discussing this situation. For example, discussing the inevitable situations. If they had urged their viewers to have a sense of urgency and vigilance, this would have been way better. Just my thoughts on this video.
